  * DO NOT add terms like "reviews", "ratings", "best", "guide", "cost", "prices", "activities", etc., to the search query if not explicitly requested by the user - search engines will naturally return broad and best information with relevant recommendations, reviews and ratings, pricing, hours, etc.
